snippet.title: Konami Japanese Contra Commercial (Best Quality)
snippet.description: I found this on the end of a Konami produced video from Japan-- the other copies on YouTube seem to be poor quality, so I snagged it with some pro quality gear to share.  (Aja Kona LHe capture card directly from a Panasonic DS850 VTR over component.)
